column1: #Text=As Jav leaped toward him Carthoris laid his hand upon the hilt of his long-sword .

#Text=The great apartment was empty save for the four at the dais , yet as Jav stepped back from the menace of the Heliumite 's threatening attitude the latter found himself surrounded by a score of bowmen .
#Text=Both Carthoris and Thuvia looked their astonishment .
#Text=Now the former 's sword leaped from its scabbard , and at the same instant the bowmen drew back their slim shafts .
#Text=Tario had half raised himself upon one elbow .
#Text=For the first time he saw the full figure of Thuvia , who had been concealed behind the person of Carthoris .
